content: Ambassadeur是斯德哥尔摩的主要俱乐部之一，距离Stureplan仅一箭之遥。在它的三个不同主题的大厅里，已经组织了几场由知名DJ，包括Steve Aoki和David Guetta等人的现场音乐会。所有大厅都有舞池和酒吧，总共可容纳900人，保证是一个难忘的夜晚。如果你想要一个史诗般的夜总会体验，想要像没有明天一样的派对，那就是你要去的 "Ambassadeur "! 每个周末，斯德哥尔摩最生动的派对人群都会涌向Ambassadeur，享受迷人的电子现场表演和充满活力的视觉效果，创造一个真正史诗般的夜店体验。周五或周六在Ambassadeur度过的夜晚将开启一个不同音乐风格的世界；客人们将体验到从最新的house-hits和R'n'B到progressive和schlager的各种音乐。这个受欢迎的地方拥有多个俱乐部、酒吧和舞池，肯定能满足各种音乐品味。如果你想把沉闷的工作日抛在脑后，像没有明天一样开派对，请加入我们的Ambassadeur。
contentEn: Ambassadeur is one of Stockholm's major clubs which is just a stone's throw from Stureplan. In its three halls with different themes have been organized several live concerts by well-known DJs including Steve Aoki and David Guetta and many more. With dance floors and bars in all halls and their total intake of 900 people it will be guaranteed a night to remember. If you want an epic nightclub experience and party like there is no tomorrow, it's the Ambassadeur you'll go! Every weekend Stockholm’s most vivid party crowd flocks to Ambassadeur to enjoy captivating electronic live sets and vibrant visual effects that create a truly epic nightclub experience. A Friday or Saturday night spent at Ambassadeur will open up a world of various musical styles; guests will experience everything from the latest house-hits and R’n’B to progressive and schlager alternatives. This popular locale boasts multiple clubs, bars, and dance floors, sure to accommodate every musical taste. If you want to leave dull weekdays behind and party like there is no tomorrow, join us at Ambassadeur.
